WEBVTT

00:01:30.042 --> 00:01:34.184
Howard proceeds to hand
my own proposal back to me.

00:01:34.208 --> 00:01:37.351
And explains to me
the many merits of what I wrote.

00:01:37.375 --> 00:01:39.792
(Laughter)

00:01:41.375 --> 00:01:44.976
Howard was never against
recruiting more women.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:47.643
But he needed to hear from a man

00:01:47.667 --> 00:01:50.708
why it was important to hire more women.

00:01:51.708 --> 00:01:54.268
And as this scene played out,

00:01:54.292 --> 00:01:56.208
I said nothing.

00:01:57.625 --> 00:02:02.976
Because I knew somehow that I was a guest